lemma split (hm : m.size = n‚āĀ + n‚āā) : ‚ąÉ m‚āĀ m‚āā, m‚āĀ.size = n‚āĀ ‚ąß m‚āā.size = n‚āā ‚ąß m = m‚āĀ + m‚āā := by
  induction n‚āā generalizing m with
  | zero =>
    subst hm;
